					<div>
					<h1 class="head">Who is invited?</h1>
					<p>This workshop is appropriate for individuals in or about to be promoted to middle- 
                		and upper-management positions of agencies that serve populations of 25,000 or 
                		more. Attendees will be exposed to a wide range of thought on the application of 
                		program subject matter by experienced administrators, educators, and 
                		practitioners. Professionals who are open to learning, analyzing and discussing 
                		new ideas for the purpose of self- and organizational-improvement will benefit 
                		most from attending.</p>
						<p>The <a href="http://www.ptb.state.il.us/">Illinois Law Enforcement Training & Standards Board</a> has approved 35 
						hours of continuing education credits for Chiefs and Deputy Chiefs.  </p>
                		
				
