</p>
<p>Mr. Furcon's representative private sector clients include: Avon, Bank of New York Mellon, BP Amoco, Citi, Discover, Doosan Infracore, Kraft, Gillette, Hershey Foods, McDonald's, Morgan Stanley, Nabisco, Panasonic, Pratt & Whitney, Rohm & Haas, Sears, UBS and United Technologies. His representative public and not-for-profit sector clients include: AMTRAK, CalPERS, City of Chicago, County of Los Angeles, Illinois State Police, TIAA-CREF, U.S. Department of Justice and U.S. Postal Service.
